Package: bc-hrbl
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Hash-Routed Binary Layout — command-line driver
 CLI driver for the `.hrbl` binary format: verify, query, inspect and
 convert. Built on libbc-hrbl: zero-copy mmap reader, parallel
 writer, integrity checker. Convert accepts --from=json (bootstrap)
 and --to={json,yaml,ini} for one-way export.
 .
 The binary format is the source of truth. Text formats are import
 (JSON via json-c) or one-way export (JSON, YAML via libyaml, INI
 hand-written).
